OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776449466
OL,3,CUltra-marathon champion from Dumfries
OL,4,Cdies while running
OL,6,FA 35-year-old champion ultra-marathon
OL,7,Frunner has died while completing the
OL,8,FCape Wrath trail.
OL,10,FDavid Parrish, from Dumfries, was
OL,11,Fattempting to become the fastest man
OL,12,Fto complete the 234 mile route from
OL,13,FFort William to Cape Wrath.
OL,15,FHis body was discovered in the north
OL,16,Fwest Highlands on Saturday night
OL,17,F(April 11), according to police.
