OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776449466
OL,3,CUltra-marathon champion from Dumfries
OL,4,Cdies while running
OL,6,FDavid was fundraising for Scottish
OL,7,FMountain Rescue at the time, in memory
OL,8,Fof his friend Luke Ireland, who passed
OL,9,Faway from hypothermia while running in
OL,10,Fthe mountains around Glen Clova.
OL,12,FTributes have been paid to the former
OL,13,FRoyal Marine by local and national
OL,14,Frunning clubs.
OL,16,FCrichton Parkrun said on Facebook:
OL,17,F"All of us at Crichton Parkrun are
OL,18,Fsaddened to learn of the death of
OL,19,FDavid Parrish while running the Cape
OL,20,FWrath ultra route.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
