PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776449466
OL,3,CUltra-marathon champion from Dumfries
OL,4,Cdies while running
OL,6,F"An event that he previously won.
OL,7,FDavid was a frequent participant in
OL,8,Four Parkrun with his little spaniel,
OL,9,Fmore often than not crossing the line
OL,10,Ffirst.
OL,12,F"We are sure you will all join us in
OL,13,Fsending love to his family and
OL,14,Ffriends."
OL,16,FThe Annan and District Athletic Club
OL,17,Fwrote: "All at ADAC were deeply
OL,18,Fsaddened to hear the news of local
OL,19,Frunner David Parrish's passing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
