OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776449466
OL,3,CUltra-marathon champion from Dumfries
OL,4,Cdies while running
OL,6,F"Our thoughts and condolences are with
OL,7,Fhis family, friends, and everyone at
OL,8,FDumfries Running club at this
OL,9,Fincredibly difficult time.
OL,11,F"Rest in peace, David."
OL,13,FThe GB Ultras Community said: "David
OL,14,Fwas an absolute gentleman, an
OL,15,Finspiration to so many and continued
OL,16,Fto push the boundaries of what is
OL,17,Fpossible while raising vital funds for
OL,18,Fcauses close to his heart.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
